类 LongParameter

  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Parameter<java.lang.Long>

    public class LongParameter
extends SimpleParameter<java.lang.Long>
    A Parameter storing a Long within min and max bounds (inclusive).

    Note that the default value may be outside of these bounds.

      • setDefaultValue

        public LongParameter setDefaultValue(long defaultValue)
        Set the default value.

        The default may set to any value and is not restricted by setting the minimum or maximum values.

        参数:
        defaultValue - the default value.
        返回:
        this

      • setMinimumValue

        public LongParameter setMinimumValue(long minimumValue)
        Set the minimum value.

        If a maximum value has been set then the minimum value must not be greater than the maximum value.

        参数:
        minimumValue - the minimum value
        返回:
        this

      • setMaximumValue

        public LongParameter setMaximumValue(long maximumValue)
        Set the maximum value.

        参数:
        maximumValue - the maximum value
        返回:
        this
